imdb.plot outline: Follows the road to the crowning of the AWA World Champion, beginning with the four Whitetail Pro Series qualifying events. Unlike other hunting competitions, AWA events use advanced digital scope technology to record kills made with blank cartridges, rewarding hunters who take shots at mature whitetail deer.
